description: Get more veg into your day with this easy zucchini muffin recipe. Nutritionally approved, these tasty muffins are the perfect snack for on the go.
keywords: Savoury muffin,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Healthier Easier,Video,Low sugar,Sesame free,Zucchini,High protein,High fibre,Peanut free
name: Easy Cheesy Zucchini Muffins Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 4.5 cups Macro Organic wholemeal spelt flour
3 large zucchini, finely grated (save 1 spiralised zucchini to decorate)

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180°C/160°C fan-forced. Line a 12-hole 1/3-cup capacity muffin pan with paper cases.
Place flour, baking powder and pepper in a large bowl and stir to combine. Add oregano, garlic, zucchini and cheese, then stir to combine and make a well in centre.
Whisk milk, eggs and oil in a bowl. Pour egg mixture into zucchini mixture and stir until just combined.
Divide mixture among cases. Top with extra zucchini and season with pepper, then bake for 30 minutes or until golden and a skewer inserted into centres comes out clean.
